        "client_msg_id": "4ce0747d-561b-45fa-98ba-8cc5e1602cd7",
        "type": "message",
        "text": "Yep! Pre-interview. I usually describe what I'm looking for: tell me about a campaign, tell me about a blog post, tell me about a web project...whatever it is..and then specifically ask that they cover things like:\n• What were the goals of the project?\n• Who were your stakeholders?\n• Who was the persona you were doing this for? how did that guide your decisions?\n• What was the most \/ least impactful part of the project? (ex: if you had to do it in half the time, what would you have cut? If you had 2x as much time, what would you have added or done more of? why?\n",
